1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:22,840
This program is recorded at Delhi on 24 November 1973. Here Shri Mataji is replying to the questions of the “sadhakas” (seekers) during the ten-day series of lectures held at Delhi.

2
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:31,560
Shri Mataji: …to your subject matter. I will just try to continue with my thoughts.

3
00:00:31,560 --> 00:00:42,000
And later on, if you have any problems, I’ll answer about them. But as I told you, it is an ocean, ocean of knowledge,and I have been speaking like this for five years.

4
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:44,380
And some of them have been hearing Me for about five years.

5
00:00:44,380 --> 00:01:03,199
But still, everything I say, they want to record it and want to re-hear it and I don’t know, soI think it is all a bottomless pit.

6
00:01:03,199 --> 00:01:19,980
Just before Kundalini, let us know what is creation.

7
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:28,440
Because without creation you do not understand the place of Kundalini. Which I will, in a very short form, tell.

8
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:55,149
The entire creation, like the tree, is the manifestation of one seed, which we can call as “Brahmabeej” ( seed of Brahma).

9
00:01:55,149 --> 00:02:02,750
Is the seed of creation.  Now every seed has a  germinating power. In the same way, the Brahmabeej also has a germinating power.

10
00:02:02,750 --> 00:02:10,650
Now it’s a hypothesis for you. For all the scientific understanding, it is a hypothesis.

11
00:02:10,650 --> 00:02:25,890
But we can establish it later on by our experiments. So, it becomes a law and a scientific fact.

12
00:02:25,890 --> 00:02:42,000
In the beginning, this seed, there is no beginning and end, but let us start from a stage, from where the seed becomes the tree and the tree becomes the seed.

13
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:54,230
The seed vibrated first time, and the vibrations of Divine Love, which is the power of that seed of Brahma.

14
00:02:54,230 --> 00:03:16,860
Also, a power that thinks, regulates, plans and creates.

15
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:30,140
You can’t conceive of such a power. Because such a power does not exist in the material world.

16
00:03:30,140 --> 00:03:45,780
So, from the seed, the vibrations of awareness started. (I think you should put your hands like this so that your de-conditioning also goes on with my speech.

17
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:54,370
) So, the vibrations of that Divine Love spread on all the sides of the seed and formed the surface.

18
00:03:54,370 --> 00:04:03,980
This is what we call as Shakti, is the power, the Divine Love. Or the Divine Power.

19
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:38,190
So, the seed was separated. The seed of Brahma, which was abstract, in the sense that it was not manifesting in any material appearances, manifestations, the seed was separated from the Shakti, and we had two forces working, one was the Brahma itself as a seed and another as its power, as the Shakti.

20
00:04:38,190 --> 00:04:51,370
They call it, the Shaivites call it as the Shiva and the Shakti. Vaishnavites call it as a Vishnu, Krishna and Radha.

21
00:04:51,370 --> 00:04:54,900
Whatever you call it, is not the point.  Actually, we human  beings only call them by names and separate them.

22
00:04:54,900 --> 00:05:15,150
But, actually, there were only two things that existed. The first, the Ishwara, the witness, the regulator, the supervisor, who was watching his own Shakti and the play of that Shakti.

23
00:05:15,150 --> 00:05:32,690
The Shakti started manifesting itself. But, the Ishwara is the supervisor; He is the witness and He is silent.

24
00:05:32,690 --> 00:05:40,800
Shakti had three powers. How She manifested, how She came into being, is another subject.

25
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:52,500
How She has managed it is another subject. But She has got three powers.

26
00:05:52,500 --> 00:06:02,870
First power is, through Her ego, which is an incarnating power. Second power is Her Divine power, and the third power is Her material power.

27
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:28,850
Divine power throughout regulated, created the whole Universe. Shakti, by another movement, created three types of moods.

28
00:06:28,850 --> 00:06:42,150
Three moods She created by movement like that.  Thrice  She moved like that, around Her ego and these three moods were, like a mother, She had a desire to have a child.

29
00:06:42,150 --> 00:07:05,520
Desire! So, She created “Tamo guna”. Then She had to act on that, so, She created the “Rajo guna”, the activating force.

30
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:08,830
And once she has created Her own creation, She wanted to reveal her love. So, the “Sattva guna” was created, the Revelation.

31
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:29,800
She is the Mother. If you can think of, She is the mother of all the mother. How a mother sees her child, She sees Her creation.

32
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:41,490
First, She creates through the Divine power, acting on the material power, all the creation.

33
00:07:41,490 --> 00:07:59,980
And then, She comes again and again, again and again, in three different forms. She comes as a mother Herself.

34
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:11,940
She has come in many forms in many parts of the world.

35
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:16,490
She came as Muhammad’s daughter, She came as Nanaka’s sister, She came as Janaka’s daughter.

36
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:34,229
Only one person all the time, coming in this world in different forms. When She comes only as a Mother, She is very different, and She is very dynamic.

37
00:08:34,229 --> 00:08:46,470
But, sometimes She comes as a wife and sometimes as a mother, then She is dormant.

38
00:08:46,470 --> 00:09:07,220
She acts, but She is not felt. Like, Radha of Krishna. Same Mother comes, again and again, incarnates to help the people to evolve out of this Bhavasagara, the void.

39
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:27,990
She creates the Maya, She creates the illusion. Like a mother, like a mother bird who hides herself and calls her little one.

40
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:29,810
The little birdie.  So, the little bird can spread its wings to  find the mother.

41
00:09:29,810 --> 00:09:46,760
She creates all the illusion. And it is She only, who make you realise that it is all an illusion.

42
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:55,950
She makes you feel that you are separate from Her.  The “I” ness in you  She develops Herself. And then She wants you to find out the means, the Mother, the all-pervading Chaitanya that is your Mother.

43
00:09:55,950 --> 00:10:17,880
And then She reveals Her love and exposes Herself, Her love into your being.

44
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:39,430
I would not like to touch that now.  Then, up to the human level it has stopped.

45
00:10:39,430 --> 00:10:44,870
Now the human being has raised his body. The animal has not.

46
00:10:44,870 --> 00:11:07,730
But human being raised his body and his brain starts developing in a conical way. That conical structure gives it a prism-like quality, by which, the Chaitanya, the light, when it pours into the brain, goes into refraction.

47
00:11:07,730 --> 00:11:09,730
I hope you understand the word refraction.  Means  it passes through the prism, as you have seen, “kendrikaran” (centralisation) they call it.

48
00:11:09,730 --> 00:11:28,570
The rays are separated. Only in the human beings, the rays of Chaitanya are separated, and not in the animals.

49
00:11:28,570 --> 00:11:39,050
And the rays that pass through the center of the fontanelle bone here, which you call as “talu”, it is a very important thing.

50
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:52,800
It passes through the apex of the brain and goes straight directly down to the medulla oblongata and settles down at the back of the triangular bone known as the coccyx.

51
00:11:52,800 --> 00:12:05,490
It is completely parasympathetic in its function, that is, it fills you up completely and that rests there as the residual consciousness.

52
00:12:05,490 --> 00:12:19,980
That is the Kundalini. Doctors may not agree today but they will have to agree one day. I can show you the breathing of the Kundalini in the coccyx.

53
00:12:19,980 --> 00:13:12,240
[Mother is talking aside to Sahaja Yogis]. So, in the centre of this, in the centre of your head, at the coccyx, from there to the coccyx, is a line which goes down through the medulla oblongata and is known as the channel of“Sushumna”.

54
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:33,370
But their channels are known as “Ida” and “Pingala”.

55
00:13:33,370 --> 00:13:45,010
So, the Mother Kundalini settles down (as) the residual consciousness in the coccyx.

56
00:13:45,010 --> 00:14:00,970
She is very well settled there, waiting for an opportunity to rise. And the opportunity is, when her child, she has only one child.

57
00:14:00,970 --> 00:14:18,300
And throughout his birth, she is following him. She is all the time there. When the child dies, her vacuum is created. And (when the child is born again), again she comes back in the same child.

58
00:14:18,300 --> 00:14:29,620
And she knows all the problems of the child. This Kundalini gives you the rebirth.

59
00:14:29,620 --> 00:14:53,250
You have heard about “dwijaha” the one who is twice-born. Every religion,every religion, I mean religion; I do not mean irreligion – every religion has preached that you have to be reborn.

60
00:14:53,250 --> 00:15:03,170
Those, who have not, are no religion. Religion in the Sanskrit language is “dharma”.

61
00:15:03,170 --> 00:15:14,510
Dharma means “dharaiticha dharma”, the one which you sustain. Whatever you sustain is the dharma. Still, sustain does’nt have that meaning, but still, you can say sustain.

62
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:19,200
Because in the law ministry and all that, you hear this word, it is too much and so cheaply.

63
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:26,630
But one that sustains is the dharma. Sustains what? Sustains the meeting of the all-pervading.

64
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:45,270
Remember one thing that all these things are not dharma.

65
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:49,260
Dharma is only the one that sustains the meeting of Atma (Spirit) with Paramatma (God Almighty).

66
00:15:49,260 --> 00:16:17,220
In the human being, in his heart, in every human being, in the heart of all the living beings, is the reflection of the Atma, which is of the Paramatma, which is the Ishwara, which I have told you about, He is reflected.

67
00:16:17,220 --> 00:16:20,300
And like a flicker of a flame, just like your thumb, it is there in your heart.

68
00:16:20,300 --> 00:16:30,100
Actually you, all your growth, creation, everything, is managed by your heart – not by your brain.

69
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:36,870
In the seat of the heart, in the centre of the heart.

70
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:45,040
Your point is all right.  The doctor says the heart is here.

71
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:54,950
The heart is the organ. The heart is the organ, which is looked after by the cardiac plexus.

72
00:16:54,950 --> 00:17:12,490
So, part of the cardiac plexus is looking after the heart. Because cardiac plexus has got many sub-plexuses.

73
00:17:12,490 --> 00:17:27,859
Out of which, except for four of them, the rest of them, that is, the heart has got twelve sub-plexuses. Out of which eight of them are looking after the heart.

74
00:17:27,859 --> 00:17:31,269
Four of them, other things, I mean, there is a mixture of all these things, some of them are looking after the heart and some of them are looking after the mind.

75
00:17:31,269 --> 00:17:54,659
But this light is in your heart, in the organ heart – not in the plexus. Plexus is for the play of the Kundalini.

76
00:17:54,659 --> 00:18:00,299
But the Kundalini moves in such a way that she goes to the heart later on and the enlightenment takes place. The spark starts from there.

77
00:18:00,299 --> 00:18:16,889
And when we raise your Kundalini through Sahaja Yoga, the system is followed like this, the Kundalini rises because of a certain condition being filled.

78
00:18:16,889 --> 00:18:32,100
There is a gap in your Sushumna, which is shown outside also, that below the heart, the vagus nerve ends abruptly. And up to the aortic plexus, there is a void.

79
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:50,429
If there is a doctor, he will understand it. This void is to be filled by the same Divine love. If somebody, who has got the Divine love flowing through her or his being, then such a person can pour that love, that water of love for your seeking journey.

80
00:18:50,429 --> 00:19:05,159
This is the condition of Sahaja Yoga. That is why a person who is not realised cannot do this.

81
00:19:05,159 --> 00:19:09,389
Even a realised person may not be able to do this.  Because he must be at a certain  stage of that Divine love by which he can give realisation.

82
00:19:09,389 --> 00:19:20,450
For example, we have given realisation to thousands of people both here and abroad and also awakening to, I do not know how many thousands.

83
00:19:20,450 --> 00:19:31,359
But out of them, only eleven people so far can give realisation. And they know the technique of giving the realisation and telling the people how to maintain it.

84
00:19:31,359 --> 00:19:39,029
Only eleven in these five years. The day I have a thousand like you, no problem.

85
00:19:39,029 --> 00:19:47,850
I need a thousand hands to fight the war between the dharma and adharma. Dharma can be established.

86
00:19:47,850 --> 00:19:55,460
But the only problem of Sahaja Yoga is that you have to be completely independent and free.

87
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:59,619
And that you must choose it by your will.  Your will will be respected till the  end. If you have no will to have it, you cannot have it.

88
00:19:59,619 --> 00:20:17,869
It is not enticement or mesmerism by which I can do it. So naturally, it will have to work slowly, gradually, according to your will.

89
00:20:17,869 --> 00:20:29,360
If you do not have the will, I am going to respect you as a mother respects her grown-up son. It is for you to decide to have it. It is in your will, you get the experience and you are sure of it.

90
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:34,830
And once you get it, there is no doubt left in your mind. You know that.

91
00:20:34,830 --> 00:21:05,010
Beg pardon?[Inaudible/question about method]. Shri Mataji: Now, in this? There are different and different types of people and different types of things they have done to their own Kundalini.

92
00:21:05,010 --> 00:21:12,859
The problem is how far you have kept your Kundalini alright. It is very important. Because it falls in many places. We have seen, we are trying to pull it up and it’s going down.

93
00:21:12,859 --> 00:21:24,169
But nothing will happen to you. You will not know a thing. Now, the method to be followed, I tell you that later on, with that course I will tell you.

94
00:21:24,169 --> 00:21:38,909
Why should you worry? You never asked to be created.

95
00:21:38,909 --> 00:21:44,559
You never asked for all this headache. Why should you worry about these things? Let the Divine look after you.

96
00:21:44,559 --> 00:22:00,529
We feel we are carrying the load of the world on our heads.

97
00:22:00,529 --> 00:22:06,690
The other day, as I told you a joke, that some villagers who were going by plane. They were told not to carry such a lot of luggage.

98
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:17,379
When they took their seats, they put all the luggage on their heads. And when they were asked, “Why are you putting the luggage on your head?”, they said, “Oh, we are trying to reduce the weight of the aeroplane”.

99
00:22:17,379 --> 00:22:30,509
The One who has created you, the One who is doing everything, the One who is pulsating your heart, every moment every minute he is looking after your breathing.

100
00:22:30,509 --> 00:22:45,259
What can you do? What method do you have to produce one plant out of one seed? One. I say, one. Human beings have no method to do anything that is living.

101
00:22:45,259 --> 00:22:55,929
But, in our ignorance, we think that we are doing something. We are doing nothing whatsoever.

102
00:22:55,929 --> 00:23:08,669
We have to be the tool of the Divine. That is why we are born on Earth. And Sahaja Yoga itself means Sahaja, means, born with you.

103
00:23:08,669 --> 00:23:24,149
In the same way, you do nothing to get realisation.

104
00:23:24,149 --> 00:23:37,650
Actually, this is a fact. And what do I do? I just love you. That’s all. If I say I love you, you might think it is a relative term, it is not.

105
00:23:37,650 --> 00:23:50,590
It is like the sunshine.  As the sun shines on you, My  love shines on you. And the love pour into your being, deconditions you, and that void is filled, and the Kundalini rises in her glory.

106
00:23:50,590 --> 00:23:54,450
But so far, all the other Kundalini jagruti (awakening) you might have heard about, you just forget them.

107
00:23:54,450 --> 00:24:04,859
[Inaudible/someone asks or comments]. Oh, just forget.

108
00:24:04,859 --> 00:24:13,480
They are so confused, to such an extent.  You may have read very, very  big books, I know. So many people have written, and I used to laugh at them.

109
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:23,659
Now, some, they are so much confused that they do not know that Mooladhara is separated very much from Mooladhara chakra.

110
00:24:23,659 --> 00:24:27,179
It is a very important point you have brought out. I wish I could tell you because you are all matured people.

111
00:24:27,179 --> 00:24:37,600
Mother is a holy thing.  You are already sublimated.

112
00:24:37,600 --> 00:24:48,990
You are not to be sublimated. Those who talk of sex sublimation are foolish people, they have no idea. You are already having your mother seated there, just waiting for this little happening.

113
00:24:48,990 --> 00:25:08,940
Mooladhara chakra is the only chakra in which is outside the medulla oblongata and is seated at a point from where it also controls your sex.

114
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:22,140
Sex is something like we have got an outlet in our household, “mori” (Marathi meaning sink). A little of that energy flows there and it is settled at Mooladhara chakra.

115
00:25:22,140 --> 00:25:48,049
Finished.  Do we, when we want to drink water,  do we pump out that mori and put up that water there – even if we do not have water to drink? How can you have evolution this way by going through sex? Sex has nothing to do with Kundalini, I can assure you that.

116
00:25:48,049 --> 00:25:59,450
On the contrary, those who try these tricks, putting the sex on their mother, are insulting their mother to such an extent that she gets angry and annoyed.

117
00:25:59,450 --> 00:26:03,399
And her temper which crawls on your sympathetic nervous system gives you all these horrible experiences of shouting, screaming, jumping and all doing all kinds of things.

118
00:26:03,399 --> 00:26:15,039
She is your mother. As an Indian, you can understandwhat is a mother Now that Freud was another of rakshasa who preached all these nonsensical things about human beings.

119
00:26:15,039 --> 00:26:27,470
He only knew about libido, he had not the complete knowledge about human beings. He just discussed libido.

120
00:26:27,470 --> 00:26:39,779
And with libido, he confused Kundalini, and he is talking about all these suppressed feelings which are nothing but expression and manifestation of the libido. Libido is just a part on the side which we call as Pingala Nadi.

121
00:26:39,779 --> 00:26:51,450
He has ruined the American mind by talking about this. And the American mothers, poor things are completely crushed under it.

122
00:26:51,450 --> 00:26:54,020
At least, thank God in India, we do not have this problem. We have many others but not this.

123
00:26:54,020 --> 00:27:12,799
If that was not there, it is a wonderful place and beautiful people just seeking realisation.

124
00:27:12,799 --> 00:27:22,070
About to get realisation. So, we as Indians understand what our mother is and putting the sex on her.

125
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:38,499
Except for Jung, who was right disciple, who has refuted allhis charges many a times and written books after books against this kind of attitude, one-sided attitude of Freud.

126
00:27:38,499 --> 00:27:51,799
But few people have read Jung. That’s the tragedy. But as it is, now this is the wrong type of Kundalini sadhana as they call it.

127
00:27:51,799 --> 00:28:08,940
She never gets angry. You do not know how much she loves. She loves you more than I do. When I try to raise your Kundalini, she says first cure my child.

128
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:16,429
This is the problem of my child of previous birth. This is the problem of my child of this birth. Physically this is the problem.

129
00:28:16,429 --> 00:28:17,639
Will you please first cure the child? So, I have to jolly well cure you, otherwise, she will not come up.

130
00:28:17,639 --> 00:28:20,869
[Inaudible/question about the position of Kundalini].

131
00:28:20,869 --> 00:28:37,629
Now, her position in the medulla oblongata is the coccyx in the triangular bone, where she sits in three and a half coils.

132
00:28:37,629 --> 00:28:50,380
Which you can see also, later on.  When you are realised  and go to a certain state. And when you have got it, through your parasympathetic and you can go your sympathetic and see all these things.

133
00:28:50,380 --> 00:28:57,009
They are so confused, if you read their books, don’t you find they are very much confused? About their positions and everything that they talk about.

134
00:28:57,009 --> 00:29:02,080
Some say the Mooladhara chakra is here and some say it is there. How can that be? Truth is only one.

135
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:09,179
[Inaudible/Tantriks?] Tantriks are another type, I do not know what to call them.

136
00:29:09,179 --> 00:29:25,840
They are harming themselves and all the rest of the world. And they will take ages to get realisation. Ages. It’s a sin they are committing.

137
00:29:25,840 --> 00:29:41,500
All the tantrikas. What is a shakti without love? There is no shakti without love. Tantriks do not know where they are, what they are doing.

138
00:29:41,500 --> 00:29:55,869
They are just doing it.  Now, as far as Kundalini  is concerned, I have covered that topic. Now, about tantrikas, as he has come, let me talk about libido because that he is interested.

139
00:29:55,869 --> 00:29:58,879
But what about meditation then? Should we talk about tantrikas tomorrow? All: Tomorrow.

140
00:29:58,879 --> 00:30:07,960
Shri Mataji: On Libido because we must have the experience, that is the main thing. Because meditation is the most important.

141
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:20,409
Realised, those who are realised understand the importance of Realisation. Because talks are talks, reading is reading and Divine is Divine. You cannot reach there with your thoughts or reading.

142
00:30:20,409 --> 00:30:55,389
On the contrary, those who have read too much, it is very difficult for me to make them understand this is all “avidya” (false knowledge How do you describe your Mother in words? Have you got enough words to even describe the material mother you have? Then how can you understand that Divine, which is the mother of all the mothers.

143
00:30:55,389 --> 00:31:08,519
It is for you to feel that love and jump into the ocean of that love which is knowledge, complete knowledge. And beauty.

